<A>__{a roll of thunder. over the heads of the audience, far above the thatched roof of the theatre, clouds are gathering in the sky. on stage "mercutio" is in 'romeo's" arms, but the tone of the playing is unlike anything we have seen before: without bombast, intense and real. and the audience is quiet and attentive.}
